name: OBEX INC./EZStudentLife
tag_list: books, online-book-store, used-books, cheap-books, social-networking, facebook-for-students, roommates-finder, rooms, classifieds
overview:
EZStudentLife.com is where students within and across school campuses trade their books and personal items at their own set price. Our free college classifieds allows students to post things to sell (rooms, cars, roommates, etc.) or find that special someone. Post and find upcoming gigs, parties, local and campus events in our event calendar. EZStudentLife.com allows students to connect with their local and campus student communities.

Our patent pending process provides live interaction between buyers and sellers within and across school campuses. Buyers and sellers can negotiate prices via audio visual and/or chat session, which is similar to face to face negotiation. EZStudentLife.com also provides ongoing interaction between the buyer and seller through a follow up and feedback process that involve bidding and counter offer.

EZStudentLife.com is 100% FREE! Basically, use it and share with your friends. Reasons to Join EZStudentLife.com

Trade your books and personal items with your fellow students
Bid, buy and find bargains on books and other personal items from your fellow students
Buy and sell unlimited books and personal items at your own set price
Meet new friends or find that special someone
Find everything you need in our campus classified (rooms, cars, roommates etc.)
Post, view and respond to various classified ads within and across campuses
Post and find upcoming gigs, parties, local and campus events
Find local businesses
Interact with fellow students via audio visual and/or chat session
Connect with campus students community and more!
Best of all, it&#8217;s 100% FREE!
